# 15) FOG / ATMOSPHERICS KIT

Use atmosphere carefully.

## Good Use
- light dust haze
- thin energy mist near saucer fractures
- subtle volumetric glow in distance

## Bad Use
- thick smoke blankets
- over-fogging the UI view
- obscuring robot silhouettes

The scene should feel cinematic, not muddy.

---

# 16) PERFORMANCE LAYOUT RULES

Since this is web-first, layout discipline matters.

## Rule A
Use a few strong hero props, not many mediocre props.

## Rule B
Repeat modular barrier walls and debris intelligently.

## Rule C
Avoid stacking too many transparent shield objects.

## Rule D
Keep background density lower than center density.

## Rule E
Use lighting and composition to imply scale, not endless objects.

