# 17) BUILD ORDER

Use this exact order.

## Step 1
Lay down ground base and perimeter boundaries.

## Step 2
Place the saucer in Z3.

## Step 3
Place the throne in Z5.

## Step 4
Block in left and right flank cover fields.

## Step 5
Add weapons and tool systems.

## Step 6
Add sponsor pillars and AFL signage.

## Step 7
Place robots.

## Step 8
Add debris and support props.

## Step 9
Set camera grid.

## Step 10
Place hotspots and CTA anchors.

## Step 11
Tune lighting and fog.

## Step 12
Remove clutter until the scene reads cleanly from all five cameras.

